## 🧪 Test Classes

### 1️⃣ MealEndpointsTests (10 tests)
**Purpose**: Test meal management functionality
**Endpoints**: GET, POST, PUT /meals
**Key Tests**:
- ✓ Create meal with valid data
- ✓ Get all meals or specific meal
- ✓ Update meal or deactivate
- ✓ Handle invalid IDs

### 2️⃣ MenuItemEndpointsTests (11 tests)
**Purpose**: Test menu item management
**Endpoints**: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE /menu-items
**Key Tests**:
- ✓ List all items and filter by today
- ✓ Create items with validation
- ✓ Update items
- ✓ Delete items
- ✓ Validate meal existence and portion counts

### 3️⃣ OrderEndpointsTests (10 tests)
**Purpose**: Test order management and state transitions
**Endpoints**: GET, POST, PUT /orders
**Key Tests**:
- ✓ List all orders or active orders
- ✓ Create orders with validation
- ✓ Verify portion count decreases
- ✓ Manage order state transitions
- ✓ Prevent invalid state changes

