## 📋 Running Tests

### Basic Commands
```powershell
# Run all tests
dotnet test UTB.Minute.WebApi.Tests

# Run specific test class
dotnet test --filter "ClassName=MealEndpointsTests"

# Run specific test
dotnet test --filter "Name=CreateMeal_WithValidData_ShouldReturnCreated"

# With verbose output
dotnet test --logger "console;verbosity=detailed"
```

### Visual Studio
1. Open **Test Explorer** (Test → Test Explorer)
2. Click **Run All Tests**

