- Reading existing resources
- Updating resources
- Deleting resources
- Filtering data

**Error Handling** (16 tests)
- Invalid resource IDs → 404 Not Found
- Invalid request data → 400 Bad Request
- Business rule violations:
  - Non-existent foreign keys
  - Negative values
  - Sold-out items
  - Invalid state transitions

**Business Logic** (Additional)
- Portion counts decrease on order
- Meals deactivated (not deleted)
- Order state transitions validated
- Menu filtered by date

